cos none of us can sing for shit.

1037
01:13:42,520 --> 01:13:44,476
And, erm...

1038
01:13:45,920 --> 01:13:47,717
Er...

1039
01:13:47,800 --> 01:13:50,189
My dad had to swerve, and...

1040
01:13:51,960 --> 01:13:54,190
And he skidded off the road.

1041
01:13:57,440 --> 01:13:58,919
And my...

1042
