bad timing!

1070
01:17:01,120 --> 01:17:02,951
(room falls silent)

1071
01:17:03,040 --> 01:17:06,794
- I'm sorry, I'm...
- An asshole is what you are!

1072
01:17:10,360 --> 01:17:12,555
Exactly right. I am.

1073
01:17:15,960 --> 01:17:18,315
You're in love with her, aren't you?

1074
01:17:22,680 --> 01:17:25,717
Exactly right. I am.

1075
01:17:35,640 --> 01:17:38,234
Someday I will probably
thank you for this,

1076
01:17:38,320 --> 01:17:41,835
